Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.77,0:23:10.11,ED English,,0000,0000,0000,,The truth is, I want to be by your side more than anyone else
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.49,0:23:15.20,ED English,,0000,0000,0000,,Let’s go take a walk in chains of love!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.24,0:03:14.96,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(700,0)\bord6\shad3\fs70\c&H5D01E2&\3c&HFCFDFC&\pos(640,530)}The Magic Academy's {\c&H71140C&\3c&HFBFBFB&}Crisis
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.24,0:03:14.96,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(700,0)\shad1\fs70\be1\c&H5D01E2&\3c&HFCFDFC&\pos(640,530)}The Magic Academy's {\c&H71140C&\3c&HFBFBFB&}Crisis
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.96,0:23:39.98,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad4\b1\fs39\pos(200,175)\c&HF0EFEC&}Next Time
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.47,0:23:39.98,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad4\b1\fs46\pos(640,445)\c&HEDEFEE&}The Flame of Atonement
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.60,0:00:33.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The battlefield is great.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.53,0:00:36.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I love the smell of humans burning.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.22,0:00:38.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can only enjoy this during war.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.20,0:00:53.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for coming, Menville-dono.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.68,0:00:55.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to borrow your strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.77,0:01:00.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My unit is filled with wild ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.42,0:01:02.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want us to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.32,0:01:13.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You heard how Tristain and Germania captured our port, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.25,0:01:16.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you're telling me to repel them?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.69,0:01:22.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I don't expect you to burn five hundred ships.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.90,0:01:25.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't like the roundabout conversations.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.11,0:01:28.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me the place I get to burn.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.22,0:01:31.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Magic Academy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.00,0:01:36.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Magic Academy?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.40,0:03:22.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so huge...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.31,0:03:45.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.02,0:03:50.11,Default-Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep it down, will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.68,0:03:52.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? No!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.08,0:03:54.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saito!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.24,0:04:07.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me out, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.32,0:04:09.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.38,0:04:11.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who do you think I am?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.43,0:04:16.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eléonore-oneesama!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.43,0:04:18.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And Saito?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.31,0:04:24.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Louise. I'll have you stay in here for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.57,0:04:26.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why, Onee-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.53,0:04:27.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Why"?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.78,0:04:30.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because of what you had said.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.04,0:04:47.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take aim!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.47,0:04:50.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.48,0:04:55.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Focus on the target!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.57,0:04:58.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In a real battle, your target moves!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.74,0:04:59.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.52,0:05:01.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're so into it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.89,0:05:04.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't imagine this is only training.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.96,0:05:07.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.59,0:05:09.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Five minute break.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.08,0:05:11.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Agnes, did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.65,0:05:14.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're quick to notice.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.38,0:05:18.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll soon be gone from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.11,0:05:24.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our Queen will be heading to the front line.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.45,0:05:27.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She will leave in seven days.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.58,0:05:34.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We, the Musketeer Force, will be going to Albion to protect Her Highness.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.41,0:05:37.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll say farewell to this academy, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.18,0:05:45.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a shame I couldn't uncover the name of the person who razed Dungletale...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.08,0:05:47.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go to the front line, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.10,0:05:49.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Front line?! What are you...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.86,0:05:52.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to help the Princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.54,0:05:56.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard everything from this plebeian.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.29,0:05:57.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saito!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.59,0:05:59.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Louise!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.88,0:06:06.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I cannot allow a daughter of the La Vallière family to go to war.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.17,0:06:11.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, what good would come out of\Nyour going when you can't use any magic?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.17,0:06:14.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay! I'd definitely be of help!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.50,0:06:19.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, Louise.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.08,0:06:23.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,War isn't as simple as you think.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.36,0:06:25.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I'm going.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.34,0:06:27.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the only one who can protect the Princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.57,0:06:29.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Silence!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.22,0:06:32.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Until you change your mind, I will not let you out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.04,0:06:34.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.09,0:06:35.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll hold onto this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.99,0:06:37.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're being tyrannical, Onee-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.04,0:06:41.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.28,0:06:43.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,L-Let me down!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.76,0:06:44.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Louise!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.53,0:06:45.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saito!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.02,0:06:46.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Onee-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.17,0:06:48.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow, ow, ow, ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.30,0:06:57.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cool your head in here for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.67,0:07:01.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep your eyes on Louise here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.86,0:07:02.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.57,0:07:05.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saito, you're going to take Eléonore-oneesama's side?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.35,0:07:09.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, but I agree with your sister this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.70,0:07:11.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's ridiculous for you to go to war.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.86,0:07:13.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saito!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.07,0:07:14.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Vallière.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.51,0:07:17.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saito-kun's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.09,0:07:17.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.12,0:07:24.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Colbert-sensei. Please provide this impudent girl with guidance.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.41,0:07:26.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.42,0:07:29.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You blockhead!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.51,0:07:32.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your sister is worried about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.01,0:07:37.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Though I'm not good with magic, if it's for Her Highness, I could do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.13,0:07:39.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll defeat the enemy forces, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.15,0:07:41.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Defeat the enemy?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.49,0:07:45.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, you'll go and {\i1}kill{\i0} the enemy?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.20,0:07:47.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't mean that...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.26,0:07:50.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"To fight for her Highness' sake."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.90,0:07:53.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"To defeat the enemy for the country's sake."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.69,0:07:57.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how you phrase it, it's still murder!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.32,0:07:59.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Colbert-sensei...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.06,0:08:07.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want my students to go through that experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.51,0:08:11.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't say you'll go to war.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.70,0:08:13.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.04,0:08:38.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It isn't fun to assault a school if there are only kids there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.07,0:08:42.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I heard there are only girls at the school right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.90,0:08:44.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Girls? That's great!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.76,0:08:46.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's capture them alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.28,0:08:50.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're all so filthy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.28,0:08:52.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't matter if they're women.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.59,0:08:55.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll bring death to them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.06,0:09:07.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.37,0:09:09.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing, I just thought I saw something move.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.03,0:09:17.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.08,0:09:22.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.53,0:09:25.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right. Get moving as we planned.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.70,0:09:26.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.76,0:09:38.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want, Tabitha?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.47,0:09:39.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Outside...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.62,0:09:41.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not even light out yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.34,0:09:42.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.92,0:09:47.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds like it...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.97,0:10:02.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.35,0:10:04.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you safe?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.58,0:10:05.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.41,0:10:08.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Two came to our rooms, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.15,0:10:09.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We took care of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.67,0:10:11.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like they're dogs from Albion.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.75,0:10:12.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Most likely.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.42,0:10:16.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, armour up and follow me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.28,0:10:22.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.01,0:10:31.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.78,0:10:35.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go check.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.33,0:10:38.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saito-kun, you stay here and protect Miss Vallière.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.11,0:10:40.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.62,0:10:46.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What... happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.46,0:11:08.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain! They have occupied the dormitory wing!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.18,0:11:10.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the students?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.59,0:11:12.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're assembling in the cafeteria...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.48,0:11:14.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...along with the faculty and staff.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.19,0:11:17.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it, they have hostages in their hands...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.43,0:11:26.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something isn't right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.16,0:11:28.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on outside?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.23,0:11:29.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about it, go to bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.90,0:11:31.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll wake you up if something happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.07,0:12:10.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To come to the academy instead of the front line...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.60,0:12:13.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like Albion's cornered.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.82,0:12:16.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Trying to be cynical, brat?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.80,0:12:19.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It all means nothing to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.99,0:12:22.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's what my employer wants.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.33,0:12:27.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see, you're only a mercenary who's moved by money.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.00,0:12:31.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Julio-kun, it's dangerous. Stop provoking him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.34,0:12:34.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me say this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.38,0:12:36.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as you don't do anything to hinder us,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.90,0:12:39.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we will not take your lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.42,0:12:40.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rest assured.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.97,0:12:44.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.30,0:12:52.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want to turn into ashes?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.28,0:12:56.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, shut it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.25,0:12:59.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.22,0:12:59.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.16,0:13:02.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You want a hostage, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.36,0:13:05.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you make due with only myself?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.85,0:13:08.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to release the students.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.30,0:13:12.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, but you won't do.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.20,0:13:15.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The country won't move for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.12,0:13:16.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How about me, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.33,0:13:20.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the first-born daughter of the La Vallière family.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.59,0:13:23.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My father is an aristocrat with influence in this country.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.33,0:13:25.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There shouldn't be any problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.48,0:13:27.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I shall become a hostage as well,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.92,0:13:30.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so please release the students.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.10,0:13:34.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I like your spirit, but two isn't enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.96,0:13:37.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I need all of the students.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.63,0:13:41.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With the lives of all the aristocrats' daughters in danger,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.35,0:13:44.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Queen Henrietta will have to give us a thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.24,0:14:06.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those inside the cafeteria, listen!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.89,0:14:09.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are Her Highness' Musketeer Force!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.01,0:14:14.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have you surrounded with my unit!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.42,0:14:16.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Release the hostages!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.60,0:14:21.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you surrender, we won't kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.38,0:14:25.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Musketeer Force, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.27,0:14:27.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have hostages in hand, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.03,0:14:35.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those in the cafeteria!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.86,0:14:39.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No... Albionians!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.09,0:14:40.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it that you want?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.58,0:14:45.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't a political target, nor are there any weapons stored here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.92,0:14:47.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is only an academy of magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.21,0:15:06.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It exploded before the signal?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.04,0:15:09.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys stay on watch here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.05,0:15:09.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.70,0:15:14.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.82,0:15:15.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An explosion?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.92,0:15:17.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Saito!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.28,0:15:21.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, Colbert-sensei told us to stay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.28,0:15:41.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm worried because he isn't coming back!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.45,0:15:43.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me back my wand.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.15,0:15:44.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.14,0:15:45.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.10,0:15:50.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see, Unlock was...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.33,0:15:53.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.06,0:15:59.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Blowing up the door, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.49,0:16:03.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It opened, so what's the big deal?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.10,0:16:04.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.65,0:16:07.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, okay, Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.29,0:16:24.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a cheap tactic.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.75,0:16:28.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Henrietta's Musketeer Force!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.79,0:16:30.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop this futile resistance!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.31,0:16:33.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Only an academy of magic?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.42,0:16:37.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then why is your Musketeer Force stationed here?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.05,0:16:44.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To Tristain, this is a treasure chest filled with people of Tristain's future.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.85,0:16:45.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.29,0:16:49.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I'll kill one person to test that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.28,0:16:50.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who should it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.34,0:16:54.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You first.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.07,0:16:58.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll show them that we're serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.87,0:17:00.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.22,0:17:02.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Agnes!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.19,0:17:04.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So she's the captain?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.28,0:17:35.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How foolish.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.67,0:17:37.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You think you can beat me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.64,0:17:42.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will not lose to a coward who takes hostages!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.92,0:17:49.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Personally, I don't like taking hostages.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.48,0:17:53.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rather than going through the trouble, I'd burn everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.88,0:17:55.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.04,0:18:09.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I burned an entire village once before.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.56,0:18:15.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The sight of the fire engulfing everything was breathtaking!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.86,0:18:19.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what's great about war.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.94,0:18:24.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.21,0:18:25.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.77,0:18:37.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one who...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.99,0:18:39.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...burned...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.04,0:18:44.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Dungletale...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.82,0:18:48.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.84,0:18:56.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They must be from Albion.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.09,0:18:58.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it, they took hostages.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.68,0:18:59.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those cowards!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.75,0:19:02.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yup, cowardly and unmerciful guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.40,0:19:08.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys sure took your time to show up, Vallière and Saito.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.97,0:19:10.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kirche, Tabitha...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.24,0:19:16.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you're a survivor of that village?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.51,0:19:19.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're one person I'll never forgive!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.74,0:19:20.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.52,0:19:26.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like you're more skilled with swords than myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.12,0:19:27.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.18,0:19:29.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're only a plebeian in the end!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.52,0:19:37.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now you're unarmed!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.97,0:19:38.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.71,0:19:51.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kirche, do you know how many of them there are?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.99,0:19:54.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think there are too many of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.49,0:19:55.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.79,0:19:57.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're skilled.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.68,0:19:58.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't look too good...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.71,0:20:01.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We need to hurry and save them.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.69,0:20:03.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shh... someone's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.60,0:20:06.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.23,0:20:08.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Colbert-sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.49,0:20:11.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you came here...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.86,0:20:13.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I looked all over for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.52,0:20:15.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei, everyone's been taken hostage.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.90,0:20:18.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.07,0:20:20.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just sent for reinforcements.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.41,0:20:22.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys get out of here now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.91,0:20:28.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Reinforcements? They have to come all the way from the palace, don't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.56,0:20:30.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've got to handle this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.42,0:20:34.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're up against professionals.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.39,0:20:36.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You won't be a match for them!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.62,0:20:38.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But what about everyone else?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.83,0:20:41.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We need to wait until the reinforcements arrive.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.19,0:20:43.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You all get out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.24,0:20:45.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need a coward.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.93,0:20:47.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to run, then please do.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.79,0:20:49.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can go.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.79,0:20:54.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you're...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.74,0:20:57.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were the captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.96,0:21:00.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unfortunately, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.11,0:21:00.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.38,0:21:04.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unfortunately, I was not.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.33,0:21:11.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was only the vice-captain at the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.25,0:21:15.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Flame Snake was the captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.83,0:21:19.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was referred to as Enjya.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.20,0:21:21.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's more cruel than myself,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.73,0:21:24.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and possessed a flame that burned everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.16,0:21:26.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.05,0:21:31.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm in search of that man myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.01,0:21:34.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That man who inflicted a wound upon me...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.22,0:21:38.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...the Flame Snake!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.00,0:21:45.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to burn that man...!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.11,0:21:49.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's all I wish for!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.13,0:23:27.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You dog!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.13,0:23:29.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We need to save everyone, fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.05,0:23:30.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Colbert-sensei is...?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.88,0:23:31.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.71,0:23:33.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zero no Tsukaima. Futatsuki no Kishi.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.67,0:23:34.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Flame of Atonement.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.80,0:23:38.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to meet me again next week, then sit tightly and wait!
